{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_01","textHome":"自从成为魔法少女，我就一直在神滨市战斗。@拥有过快乐，但记住的却都是悲伤与心酸。@这是因为这类记忆更容易被记住吧……@但我一定要继续活下去。如果在这里放弃，@就等于否定了过往自己所坚持的这条路。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":301}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_18","textHome":"居然能做到这样……自己都有点吃惊。@比起所预想的，原来自己还能有更多潜力……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":0}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":201,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_19","textHome":"了解了……我还能提升自己。"}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_20","textHome":"感觉还有上升的动力。挺不错。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100200,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_21","textHome":"对于当了很多年魔法少女的我来说，@也许“经验”才是最大的魔法。@今后要更善于在战斗中利用这份“经验”……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":301}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":100200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1002_00_22","textHome":"在思考之前身体就自然地行动了。@仿佛脑海中的记忆